Commentary: Starts off with a fuller one on leg, Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.

OUT! BOWLED! A change of length. On a good length and on middle swinging it in, Mahmudul Hasan Joy tries to block it but misses as the ball hits the stumps. Joy's feet went nowhere and he ended up paying the ultimate price. What a start for Kasun Rajitha and Sri Lanka! The first blow for Bangladesh as Mahmudul Hasan walks off without any Joy.
Howout: b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: On a length and outside off, Najmul Hossain Shanto leaves it alone.

Sticks to his length and outside off, Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to defend it but gets a thick outside edge. The ball races towards the third man region. A couple of runs taken and the hosts are up and running in the match.
FOUR! This is a brilliant shot. Goes fuller this time, Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it right back past the bowler for a boundary. A much-needed one for Bangladesh.
On a length and outside off, this is left alone.
Fuller one swinging it outside leg, Tamim Iqbal tries to flick it but misses.
On off, this is blocked out.
A good-length delivery outside off, Taijul Islam tries to defend it but misses. The ball goes towards the keeper.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ohh, this is misery for Bangladesh. Goes fuller and on middle, Tamim tries to flick it towards square leg but gets a leading edge. The ball goes towards backward point where Praveen Jayawickrama takes a brilliant catch diving to his right and taking it with both hands. Bangladesh lose both of their openers in the starting two overs and Fernando is elated.
Howout: c Praveen Jayawickrama b Asitha Fernando

Commentary: FOUR! Fuller and on middle, Mominul Haque flicks it towards deep square leg. The ball races past the fence for a boundary.
On a length and outside off, Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Fuller and outside off, this is defended towards silly point. A quick single taken.
On a length and outside off, Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
Similar to the last delivery, this is left alone towards the keeper.
Sticks to his length bowling it outside off, Mominul Haque leaves it alone.
FOUR! A touch fuller one on off, Mominul Haque drives it off the front foot through covers for a boundary. This was a brilliant and a well-timed shot.
Goes fuller and angles it across off, this is left towards the keeper.
On a length and outside off, this is left alone.
Sticks to his length bowling it outside off, this is left towards the keeper.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
Back of the length and on off, Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it solidly.
On a length and outside off, Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to defend but gets an inside edge. The ball rolls towards the keeper.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards Asitha Fernando. First maiden over of the match.
On a length and on middle, this is defended towards silly point. A quick single taken.
Goes fuller this time and on middle, this is blocked out.
Sticks to his length and on off, this is pushed towards covers.
Goes fuller this time and on middle, this is blocked out.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
On a good length, this is defended towards covers.

OUT! CAUGHT! On a length and on off, Mominul Haque tries to defend it but gets in two minds. Puts his bat in the end and gets a bottom edge. The ball goes in the gloves of Niroshan Dickwella who makes no mistake. Third blow for Bangladesh and they need some good partnership to get the game going.
Howout: c Niroshan Dickwella b Asitha Fernando

Commentary: On a length outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
A good length delivery on middle, slightly quicker, this is blocked out. This is good bowling from Asitha Fernando.
FOUR! Fuller and wide outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim waits for the ball and uses his feet. The ball races past backward point for a boundary.
On a length and on middle, this is driven towards covers. A good chase from the fielder saving a run for his team. Three runs taken.
Sticks to his length, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
On off, this is blocked out.
Fuller and on off, Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to drive it but hits the lower part of the bat.
Goes fuller and outside off, this is left alone towards the keeper.

OUT! BOWLED! Big big trouble for Bangladesh. Fuller and on around off, swinging it inside, Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to drive it but misses as the ball hits the off pole that goes flying. Poor shot from Najmul Hossain Shanto, looking to drive at a ball that wasn't a half-volley and also keeping a gap between bat and the stumps.
Howout: b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: OUT! LBW! On a length and on middle, Shakib tries to block it but misses as the ball hits his pads. A loud appeal and the finger goes up. Shakib Al Hasan goes for a quick review. Ultra edge shows that no bat is involved. Ball tracking shows that it is pitching outside off and going on to clip the leg stump. Umpires call and Shakib has to walk away. Goes for a golden duck and pressure piling up for Bangladesh as it is just the seventh over and 24/5 now! Kasun Rajitha on a hat-trick now!
Howout: lbw b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: Rajitha steams in and bowls it fuller, around off, once again looking to swing it into the batter's pads. Litton Das solidly blocks it off and survives the hat-trick delivery.

On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim gets in two minds and tries to defend it but gets his bat out at the very last moment. The ball goes towards the keeper. Bangladesh is feeling a lot of pressure now.
On a length and outside off, this is left alone.
On off, this is defended towards backward point.
FOUR! Fuller and on off,  Mushfiqur Rahim drives it through extra covers. The fielder gives it a chase but can only escort the ball towards the fence.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
Similar to the last delivery, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it towards the keeper.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das plays it towards backward point.
Fuller one outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone.

A touch fuller and on middle and there's a bit of late swing away from the batter as well. Litton Das tries to defend it but gets an outside edge. It just fell short of the fielder at second slip. Litton Das with a lucky escape there
On middle, this is eased towards covers.
On a length and outside off, this is left towards the keeper.
Fuller and on middle, Litton Das fumbles a bit but blocks it out. There was a slight appeal from Kasun Rajitha but there was bat involved.
Outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it towards the keeper.
Back of the length angling it in on off stump, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to block it but misses. This is tremendous bowling from Asitha Fernando.
On a length and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards fine leg for one.
On off, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim with a weird drive shot but the timing was good. It races past point. Good commitment from the fielder chasing it and saving a couple for his team.
On middle, this is flicked towards deep square leg for one.
Rajitha serves it fuller and around off, Rahim goes back and across before making an assured leave.
An action replay of the previous delivery as Rajitha keeps floating it up and Rahim keeps leaving it alone.
Length this time, closer to the off pole. Rahim lets it through to the keeper.
Fuller and on off, Rahim with a front-foot punch towards the cover region.
Angling it into the pads, Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it past square leg for a single.
Good change-up! Banged in short with not much pace behind it and outside off. Litton Das looks to pull but is a bit too early in his shot.
Starts off with a floater, on middle. Rahim drives it towards extra cover.
This is a bit flatter and sliding into middle and leg. Rahim nudges it onto the leg side.
On middle, defended off the front foot.
Slowed up a touch and bowled on a nagging length on off. Rahim goes on the back foot to keep it out.
Flighted around middle. Blocked out.
Sliding in off a length, Rahim wrists it to short mid-wicket. Tidy start from Praveen Jayawickrama as he starts off with a maiden.
Litton Das is off the mark! This is very full and on middle, Das with an on drive past mid on for a couple of runs.
Pitched up, on off. Das pushes it back to the bowler.
Right on the money! Around the top of off, Das defends it onto the off side.
Fullish delivery, pushed outside off. No shot offered by Litton Das.
Rajitha pulls back the length a bit and angles it into middle and leg. Das looks to flick but gets an inside edge onto the pads. The ball rolls towards backward square leg as a single is taken.
On a length, on the fifth stump line. Easy leave there for Mushfiqur Rahim.
On off, blocked out.
FOUR! Jayawickrama just drops it a bit short and Das is lightning quick to rock back and latch onto it. Das cuts it behind square on the off side for a boundary.
Pushed through a bit quicker and outside off, left alone.
Shorter this time, around middle. Das uses the crease and tucks it behind square on the leg side for a single.
FOUR! Jayawickrama just loops it up and serves a low full toss around off. Mushfiqur Rahim gets low and just eases it through extra cover for a well-timed boundary.
Flatter, on off. Rahim with a solid punch but finds the man at extra cover.
Beaten! Perfect length, around off and this one skids through. Litton Das goes for the cover drive but is beaten past the outside edge.
Around the hips, nudged away through square leg for a run.
Length, on off and Rahim gets squared up a bit as he edges it down with soft hands towards gully.
A bit wider from Fernando, Rahim doesn't play at it.
On a good length, over off. Rahim defends it off the back foot.
And again! Length, close to the off pole, solidly blocked off by Rahim.
Nicely flighted, drifting into middle. Das defends it out.
This is drifted onto middle and leg, Das nudges it out towards short leg.
Jayawickrama is getting a nice drift in now. A bit quicker and the length is pulled back. This one drifts into the pads and Litton Das gets all squared up.
Slowed up a touch, on middle. Blocked out.
This is looped up on off, Das defends it under his eyeline.
Jayawickrama drops it short and outside off. Litton Das rocks back to cut it in front of square on the off side. The fielder from cover chases it down and keeps it down to a couple.
Ouch, that must have hurt! Asitha Fernando bangs it in short and on leg stump. Mushfiqur Rahim tries to duck under it but the ball doesn't rise up much and Rahim gets hit on the left shoulder.
Back of a length, on off. Rahim hops back and just dabs it down with soft hands towards backward point.
Fuller and angling into middle. Rahim defends it back to the bowler.
A length ball, a fair bit outside off, Rahim shoulders arms.
Length, nipping back in from outside off. Rahim gets a good stride across and blocks it out.
Back of a length, on off. This is kept out off the back foot.
Ooh, that kept really low! Jayawickrama drifts it into the pads, Das gets pushed onto the back foot but gets beaten by the lack of bounce and the ball crashes into the pads.
On middle, blocked out.
On a length, around off. Das can't get it away.
Tossed up, fuller and on off. Litton Das with a punch towards short cover where the fielder makes a half-stop.
On off, kept out.
Nicely drifted into middle and leg. Das watchfully keeps it out. End of a maiden from Jayawickrama.
Good early call from Mushfiqur Rahim and gets the single with ease. Full and around off, driven to the left of mid off for a quick run.

FOUR! Shot! Banged in short, over off. Litton Das pulls it along the ground and in front of square. There is a man on the mid-wicket fence but he has no chance, boundary! The fifty is up for Bangladesh.
Good-length, on off. Das pushes it towards wide mid on for one.
Length ball, outside off. Well left by Mushfiqur Rahim.
Fuller and shaping into middle. Rahim solidly defends it out.
Length this time, on off. Rahim taps it towards the cover region.
Flatter, sliding into middle. Das backs away and cuts it to cover-point.
On a length, on off and this one doesn't drift in. Das keeps it out.
On middle, Das drive sit to mid on.
Flatter this time, on off. Das pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated up, around off. This is driven but straight to the man at deep cover.
On the pads, just nudged away with soft hands through mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Tossed up on middle, this is eased towards mid-wicket for one.
FOUR! This is a great placement. On middle, Litton Das flicks it towards mid-wicket for a boundary.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
FOUR! Floated up on middle. A low full toss, Litton Das strikes it through mid-wicket again for a boundary. An absolute gift from Ramesh Mendis.
Goes fuller this time and on middle, this is blocked out.
On off, this is eased towards point for a single.
Tossed up of off, this is left alone.
On middle with a bit of turn, Litton Das tries to block it bit misses.

Goes fuller and on middle, this is defended towards mid-wicket.
Flatter and on middle, this is pushed back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Floated up and on middle, Litton Das defends it towards silly point.
Back of the length outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim raises arms as the ball goes towards the keeper. A slight halt in play as Kusal Mendis holds his chest and looks a bit uneasy.
Goes fuller and on leg, this is flicked towards mid-wicket for one.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
Similar to the last delivery, Litton Das raises his arms as it goes towards the keeper.
Sticks to his length bowling it outside off, Litton Das leaves it out.
Fuller and on off, this is defended away. That will be lunch for the day.
Tossed up outside off, this is eased towards silly point.
On off, blocked out.
Goes fuller this time, this is defended towards covers.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
On middle, this is defended solidly.
FOUR! A low full toss on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim opens up and flicks it through mid-wicket for a boundary. This was a poor delivery from Praveen Jayawickrama after five good deliveries.
Outside off, Litton Das raises arms as it goes towards the keeper.
On the pads. On a length and on off, Litton Das tries to defend it but hits his pads. A slight appeal from Kasun Rajitha but the finger stays down. Seemed a bit high.
On middle, this is defended back towards Kasun Rajitha.
Goes full and outside off, Litton Das leaves it towards the keeper.
Bye! Down the leg side, Litton tries to flick it but misses. Good job from the keeper who gets a glove on it. Single taken.
Goes full and outside off, this is left alone.
Flatter one on leg, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
On leg, Mushfiqur Rahim gives a slight flick as the ball goes towards fine leg. Single take.
FOUR! A poor delivery from Praveen Jayawickrama. Fuller and on middle, Litton Das pulls it through deep square leg for a boundary.
On middle, this is pushed back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Similar to the last delivery, this is again defended toward the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das raises arms as the ball goes towards the keeper.
A change in length. A rare shorter one from Kasun Rajitha, this is pulled towards square leg for one.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone. The ball just aired past the stumps.
FOUR! Fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim just gives a fine tickle as the ball races past fine leg for a boundary. Runs are raining for Bangladesh post lunch.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim raises arms and leaves it alone.
Tossed up on off, this is eased towards covers.
Floated one on off, this is defended towards extra cover.
Loopy one outside off, this is eased towards silly point.
Outside off, this is left alone.
Change of length and goes down the middle, this is defended solidly.
A maiden over. Fuller and on middle, this is blocked out.
On the pads. On a length and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to defend it but hits his pads.
Sticks to his length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
On middle, slightly quicker, this is defended towards mid-on.
Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it back towards Kasun Rajitha.
Fuller and of leg, Mushfiqur Rahim couldn't reach it as it goes in the gloves of the keeper.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Tossed up on middle, this is blocked out.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Sticks to his length and pack, Litton Das defends it solidly.
On middle, this is defended towards short leg.
Goes full and outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone. A good over so far from Praveen Jayawickrama.
A maiden over. Keeps bowling it slower and on middle, Litton Das eases it towards mid-on.
Goes full and outside off, this is defended towards covers.
Shorter and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim leans back a bit and leaves it towards the keeper.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it but gets a slight inside edge. Nothing to worry about.
On a length and on middle, this is pushed towards mid off.
Shorter one on off, Mushfiqur Rahim ducks under it.
A change of length. Goes full and on middle, this is nudged towards fine leg for one.
On middle, slightly shorter, this is eased towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up on off, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards covers.
Goes full and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Tossed up on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes full and on off, this is eased towards covers.
A maiden over. Outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
On a length and outside off, Litton Das finds a gap and pushes it through covers for a brace.
Back of the length, Litton Das goes on his back foot and punches it through covers. A couple of runs taken.
On a length and outside off, Litton Das cuts it to the point. It goes straight to the fielder.
On a length and on middle, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.
On a good length and outside off, Litton Das tries to cut it but misses.
FOUR! This is a brilliant shot. Fuller and outside off, Litton Das drives it through covers for a boundary. Bangladesh is getting a hang of the game now.
Tossed up outside off, this is eased towards silly point.

FOUR! On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to loft it over mid off but gets a lucky outside edge. The ball goes over the fielder on covers for a boundary. Not quite where he wanted to play it but the result goes his way.
On middle, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and blocks it out.
On middle, this is defended towards off side.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim opens up and drives it to covers.
Similar to the last delivery, Mushfiqur Rahim again, drives it to covers.
Back of the length and on leg, Litton Das pulls it towards backward square leg for one.
A bouncer on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to pull it but misses.
Shorter one again, Mushfiqur Rahim ducks under it.
Shorter one again, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it towards silly point.
Shorter one on off, Mushfiqur Rahim pulls it towards square leg and does it well to keep it down. Single taken.
Keeps bowling it shorter on middle, Litton Das does well and pulls it towards square leg for one.
Tossed up on off, Das pushes it to covers.
Gives it air and lands it on off, kept out.
Attacks the stumps and lands it on off, Das plays it back to the bowler.
Gives it nice air again and bowls it on off, no purchase for the left-arm spinner. Defended.

FOUR! That is a wonderful shot! Pure timing and a lot of elegance! Shorter and around off, Das rocks back and pushes it through covers for a boundary. 100 up for Bangladesh. Really good recovery courtesy these two but still a long way to go.
So just the boundary from the over then! On middle, Das defends it back towards the bowler.
Bangs this one short, at a good pace. Rahim though ducks under it.

FOUR! That is a really good shot in the end. For a second, we felt he was trying to bail out but he meant to hit it there. On middle, shortish. Rahim plays a half-pull, it goes past mid on and into the fence. He just checked his shot at the end.
Yet another short one on middle, Rahim lets it go over him.
Yet another short one on middle, Rahim rocks back and pulls it through square leg. Rolls his wrists and keeps it all along the ground. One taken.
From around the wicket now to Das but the length is short again. Left alone.
A harmless nut to end then! Down the leg side. Left alone.
Floats it up on off, this is pushed to covers.
Tossed up on off, Rahim defends.
Angled into the pads, Rahim plays the sweep shot he loves but to square leg.
On middle, Rahim lunges and keeps it out.
On off, this is pushed to cover.
A little too full this time, Rahim strokes it to covers.

DROPPED! A chance immediately after the break and it is not taken! The plan to keep bowling short almost works. Short and on middle, Das looks to pull but fails to get on top of the bounce. It goes off the top edge towards square leg. The sub, Kamindu Mendis, runs back and looks to take it but spills it. Not the easiest of chance but should have taken it. Maybe the fine leg fielder could have run in and taken it. It could have been a lot easier for him but Mendis probably called for it early. How costly will this prove?
A short one again, left alone.
Another one on the shorter side, not played at.

Just over! All of a sudden, the batters look in trouble here. This is short again, this one gets big on the batter, Rahim looks to play it on the off side, it goes off the splice and just over the leaping gully fielder for one.

FOUR! Put away! There is no backing down from Das! He was dropped earlier in the over but is not shying away from playing the pull and does so brilliantly here. 50 for him. A brilliant knock under immense pressure. Walked out when Bangladesh were 5 down for nothing and has played a vital role in taking them to safer shores. Needs to go on though. This is short and on middle, it is pulled hard and wide of square leg for a boundary.

FOUR! To the right of the square leg fielder now! That dropped catch is already hurting Bangladesh! Shorter and on middle, Das gets on top of the bounce and pulls it through backward square leg for another boundary. End of an action-packed over. A really good one for Bangladesh in the end.
On middle, blocked.
FOUR! Runs are flowing after the break! This is short and on middle, Rahim rocks back and pulls it through mid-wicket for another boundary.
Rahim will feel he missed out! This is short and outside off, Rahim cuts but to point.
Shorter and on off, Rahim pushes it to covers.
Darts it on off, defended.
Flighted delivery, on middle, Rahim keeps it out.
Flatter and on off, defended.
On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
A little too full, Das flicks it to mid-wicket.
On the pads, this is nudged around the corner for one.
On the pads, Rahim clips it to short leg.
On the fuller side again, this is flicked to mid-wicket. End of a tidy first over from Dhananjaya de Silva!

FOUR! The 100-run stand is up! An outstanding partnership. The two put on a brilliant stand in the last game and have done so here again. Mendis is not have the best of times here. He is greeted with a boundary! Shorter and on middle, this is pulled through mid-wicket and into the fence.
On middle, defended.
Flatter and on off, Das hangs back and keeps it out.
Goes short again but this time it is pulled to deep square leg. Only one.
That is a huge appeal! That though was never going to be out. The Lankan players probably felt it was off the boot! Fuller and outside off, Rahim jams it back to the bowler.
Shorter and on off, Rahim guides it to point.
Fuller and on middle, this is played to covers.

FOUR! Finds the gap and brings up his 26th Test fifty! He just loves playing against the Lankans. A 100 in the last game and now a fifty. A ton is the offer here too. Tossed up on off, this is driven past covers for a boundary.
On middle, kept out.
Rahim misses out! Shorter and outside off, Rahim cuts but to point.
Flatter and on middle, kept out.
Attacks the stumps agian. Kept out.
On off, Litton Das eases it towards mid on.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards square leg for one.
Goes fuller and outside off, Litton Das puts his pads forward and defends it.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das gets on his knees and smashes it towards fine leg. Just a single taken.
Sticks to his length, this is eased towards square leg.
On a good length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards square leg and takes a single.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Flatter and outside off, this is left alone.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is kept out.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Sticks to his length and pace, this is defended solidly.
A maiden over. On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out solidly.
On off, blocked out.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is eased back towards Ramesh Mendis.
On a length and on leg, Litton Das flicks it towards fine leg for one.
Goes full, this is defended towards silly point.
Fires it on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it towards mid on for one.
On a good length and on middle, Litton Das leans forward and blocks it away.
Flatter one on off, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and defends it.
Outside off, this is driven towards mid off.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
FOUR! On a good length and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and lofts it over extra cover for a one bounce boundary. This was effortless.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards the mid off region.
Tosses it up on middle, this is defended towards square leg.
On a length and on off, Litton Das flicks it towards mid-wicket for one.
On middle, this is eased towards mid on for one.
Gos fuller and on middle, Litton Das gets on his knees and hits it towards square leg.
Sticks to his line and length, Litton Das eases it towards mid on for a single.
Fuller and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards mid-wicket and takes a single.
Loopy one on middle, this is pushed back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Fuller and on leg, that was an attempted sweep but couldn't make adequate contact. the ball rolls past keeper.
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
Outside off, slightly quicker on pace, this is defended towards covers.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
A low full toss on off, this is eased towards covers.
Sticks to his length, Litton Das flicks it to square leg for one.
On middle, this is defended out.
Fuller and on leg, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
Fuller and on middle, Litton Das works it towards mid-wicket and rotates the strike.
Darts it on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it to mid on.
Tossed up delivery outside off, Litton Das drives it to point and gets a single.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim stays in his crease and defends it towards silly point.
A low full toss, Mushfiqur Rahim smashes it to mid-wicket. It goes straight towards the fielder.
On middle, blocked out.
Goes fuller and on off, this is defended towards covers.
Fuller and on leg, slightly slower, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for one.
Tries to swing it away from Mushfiqur Rahim outside off, this is left alone.
On off, defended out.
On a length and middle, this is blocked out towards silly mid on.
Sticks to his length bowling it outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Slower one on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it back towards the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, this is eased towards covers.
On middle, blocked out.
Goes fuller and outside off, this is defended solidly.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for one.
Tossed up on off, Mushfiqur Rahim makes room and cuts it to point.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim leans across and defends it solidly. That will be the tea break for Day 1.
Starts off with a floater on middle, Das hangs back and nudges it past square leg for one.
Looped up, on leg stump and staying a bit low. Rahim tucks it behind square on the leg side for one more.
Flatter this time, on off. Das defends it out.
Dhananjaya de Silva slides this one across the right-hander but Das manages to keep it out.
Drifted onto the pads, worked through square leg for a run.

Nicely played! A touch shorter, sliding across off. Mushfiqur Rahim goes back in his crease and cuts it really late. The ball slows down as it goes towards the third man fence and the fielder is able to cut it off. Three runs taken.
A length ball on middle and leg, Rahim pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Nicely bowled! Right around the top of off and shaping in a touch. Mushfiqur Rahim gets behind the line of the ball to make the block.
Goes fuller this time, on the fifth stump line. Rahim shoulders arms.
Banged in short outside off. Once again there's a bit of a tennis-ball bounce on offer and Rahim gets his head out of the way.
Rajitha delivers this one from wider of the crease but can't get it tight enough on off stump. Easy leave for Rahim.
Rajitha starts off with a maiden! Fuller and wider, no shot offered by Rahim.
Floated up around the leg stump, Das flicks it to short mid-wicket.
Gives it a bit more air this time, around leg. Das strides out and pushes it to mid-wicket.
Shorter, on middle. Litton Das rocks back and just nudges it past short leg for a single.
Tossed up, very full and on middle. Rahim drives it straight back to the bowler.
Flighted, on off. Rahim looks to use his feet but can't get it past the bowler.
Flatter delivery, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim with another late cut. This time the fielder from the backward point fence runs around and cuts it off. Two taken.
Short, angled into the body from 'round the wicket. Das half-pulls it towards deep backward square leg for a single.
Short again, this time from over the wicket and on off. Rahim ducks under it.
Switches to 'round the wicket again and angles across a fuller delivery, well wide of the off stump. Left alone.
Good short delivery! A steep bouncer over middle and angling across. Rahim does well to sway his head away from the ball.
Short and wide, from over the wicket and this is punched through covers for a couple of runs.
Top shot! Pitched up around off, Mushfiqur Rahim with a glorious straight drive past mid off but the outfield isn't the quickest. The fielder hunts it down and the batters come back for the third.
A touch shorter, on off. Rahim plays it off the back foot towards cover-point for a quick run.
Too easy at the moment for these two. Slanted across off, Das just caresses it behind point for a single.
Flighted delivery, on the pads. Rahim drives it through wide mid on and picks up a single.
Slower and shorter, outside off. This is cut away to deep cover for one more.
Around middle and leg, nudged away leg side.
Tossed up on leg stump, Rahim turns it through mid-wicket to make it five singles in the over.
This is angled in fuller onto middle and leg. Rahim with a solid drive towards mid on.
Right on the money! On off, Rahim defends it out.
Rajitha tries to attack the pads but drifts down the leg side, Rahim flicks it to fine leg for a run.
Back of a length, on off. Das punches it off the back foot through covers for a single.
Length again, slanted into middle. Rahim blocks it out.
Goes fuller this time, on middle. Rahim pushes it towards mid on.

FOUR! A long hop to start off a new spell from Jayawickrama and he is punished. Short, on off, Litton Das rocks back and short-arm jabs it through mid-wicket for a boundary. The partnership goes past 150!
Short and wide, cut away through covers for a couple of runs.
Good stop! Tossed up, on middle and leg, driven but straight towards the man at wide mid on.
Jayawickrama comes from over the wicket and spears it into the pads, Das nudges it on the leg side.

FOUR! Drops it short again, on leg stump. Litton Das gets down on one knee and swats it into the square leg fence, almost cleaning up the short fine leg fielder in the process. Very ordinary bowling from Jayawickrama.
FOUR! Poor over, 14 coming off it. Shorter and around leg stump, Das repeats the trick from the previous delivery and finds the fence yet again.
Length ball, around the top of off. Blocked out.
Length again, a touch wider too. This is tapped through cover-point for an easy single.
Shorter and down leg, Das lets it through to the keeper.
WIDE! Attempted bumper, way too high though from Asitha Fernando. Wide called for height.
Sri Lanka playing into the hands of Litton Das at the moment. Shorter and on off, this is pulled well in front of square on the leg side for a brace.
Fernando keeps it shorter and on middle this time. Das pulls hard but finds the fielder at square leg.
This is very full and very wide, left alone. Litton Das inching closer to a century here.
On a length, on off and skidding through. Rahim blocks it off.

NOT OUT! The skipper comes into the attack and almost picks up a wicket but it was always going down leg. Length ball, on off and nipping back in sharply off the surface. Mushfiqur Rahim gets pegged back and misses the ball as he looks to block. Rahim gets rapped on the pads and Dimuth Karunaratne does review it. No spike on UltraEdge and Ball Tracking shows that it is missing leg stump. Review lost for Sri Lanka.
FOUR! Just a tickle! Drifted onto the pads, Rahim with a delicate tickle. The ball runs away fine and into the fine leg fence.
On off, blocked out.
Short of a length, on middle. Rahim tucks it away off the back foot past square leg for one.
fullish delivery, on off. Das strides out to defend.

Sweetly timed! A gentle half-volley outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leans into it and creams it through extra cover. The doesn't have the legs to run away into the fence but they do come back for the third. 200 up now for Bangladesh.
Short ball, over middle, pulled away hard to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Staying a touch low. Length ball, on off. Rahim looks to defend but gets it off the toe end back onto the deck.
Around off, Rahim stays solid in defense.
Full and on leg stump, clipped away through mid-wicket for a run.

Overthrows and that's the HUNDRED! Short ball, on the body. Litton Das flicks it towards backward square leg for a quick run. A wild throw comes in from the fielder and there's no one backing up at the bowler's end. The ball runs away into the fence and Das gets to a magnificent ton. What an innings under pressure this has been!
On a good length, around off. This is punched away towards cover-point.
Length again, on off. This is pushed back to the bowler.
Fuller delivery, reversing a bit back into the batter. Das solidly defends it out.
Full again, angling into middle. This is flicked straight to mid-wicket.
Drifted onto the pads, flicked away past backward square leg for a single.
Very full and outside off, left alone.
Length ball, outside off. No shot offered by Das.
FOUR! Litton Das has dealt with the short ball really well today. Short and on the body, Das swivel-pulls it and beats the man at fine leg to pick up another boundary.
Banged in short, from 'round the stumps but way down leg. Left alone.
Good delivery! Fernando finds the block-hole this time on middle and Das just about jams it out.
SIX! Hammered away! Short again, around leg but it's just not short enough. Litton Das picks it up and dispatches it over the square leg fence for a biggie.
Fernando continues with the short stuff, around the body this time. Das pulls it behind square for a single. The partnership is now worth 196, staggering!
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone.
Flatter one on leg, Litton Das tries to flick it but gets an outside edge. The ball goes towards backward point. Single taken.
Leg bye. On a length and on leg, Litton Das tries to flick it but hits his pads.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das flicks it to backward square leg for one.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone
Darts it outside leg, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
On off, this is eased towards point.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Tossed up on middle, this is driven towards covers for one. 200 partnership comes up for Mushfiqur Rahim and Litton Das.
Fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it through square leg for one.
On a length outside off, Litton Das cuts it towards point for one.
On off, defended out.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Similar to the last delivery, this is pushed again towards Dimuth Karunaratne.
Goes fuller and outside off, Litton Das cuts it towards point.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
Similar to the last delivery, Litton Das leaves it alone towards the keeper.
On off, this is defended towards mid off.
Flatter one outside off, this is left alone.
Tossed up outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim drives it towards covers for one.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Goes fuller and outside off, this is eased towards point.
On off, this is blocked towards the covers.
FOUR! A full toss on middle, Litton Das lofts it over mid on for a boundary. Spoils the over a full toss on the last ball.
Tossed up on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it to short leg.
On off, this is eased towards mid-wicket.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it to point.
Goes fuller and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it towards mid on and gets a single.
Fuller and on off, the ball gets an uneven bounce and hits the pads of Litton Das.
Goes fuller and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for one.
Tossed up on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das guides it through point. The fielder gives a good chase and saves a couple for his team.
On middle, this is pushed through covers for one.
On a full length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it towards backward square leg for one.
On a full length, Litton Das drives it straight to the fielder on covers.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Tossed up on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards mid on for one.
Tossed up on middle, Litton Das defends it towards silly point.
On leg, Litton Das tries to defend it but misses as the ball hits his pads. A loud appeal from Ramesh Mendis but the finger stays down.
On middle, defended out.
Similar to the last delivery, Litton Das pushes it back towards Ramesh Mendis.
Tossed up on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it towards mid off and rotates the strike.
Goes fuller and on off, this is driven towards covers.
On a length and on off, Litton Das pushes it back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
On off, defended towards covers.
Sticks to his line nad length, Litton Das eases it towards silly point.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das leaves it towards the keeper.
Tossed up on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim gives a fine tickle as the ball rolls past fine leg. A couple of runs taken. Mushfiqur Rahim on 95 now.
On middle, this is eased towards mid on for one.
On middle, blocked out.
Fuller and on middle, Litton Das eases it towards square leg.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das gets on his knees and guides it towards square leg for one.
On middle, blocked out solidly.
Tosses up outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das sweeps it towards square leg for one.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim guides it towards square leg for one. Mushfiqur Rahim on 97 now.
Fuller and of off, Litton Das tries to defend it but misses. The ball just aired past the stumps.
On off, blocked out.
Goes fuller and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to block it but hits his pads. A loud appeal from Ramesh Mendis but the umpire is uninterested.
On a length and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it towards third man. Gets a couple of runs. Mushfiqur Rahim on 99 now!
On leg, this is defended towards short leg.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.

100 for Rahim! What a player he has been for Bangladesh! Consecutive tons and both come when his team needed it the most. He is elated and so is the crowd here. Absolutely stunning. Took his time at the start but once he got his eye in, scored freely. Gets there by guiding this short ball towards point for one. Takes his helmet off and soaks in the applause. Can he make this into a big ton now?
Goes fuller and outside leg, Litton Das leaves it alone.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller and on off, this is driven towards point
On middle, blocked out.
On off, Mushfiqur Rahim drives it through point for a single.
Fuller and outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone.
Similar to the last delivery, Litton Das leaves it towards the keeper.
Tossed up on middle, this is defended towards mid on.
On off, blocked out.
Goes fuller and outside leg, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to sweep but misses.
Goes full and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim guides it towards point.
On a length and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg.
Goes fuller and on middle, Litton Das defends it towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it towards point.
FOUR! Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim slogs sweeps it through mid-wicket for a boundary.
On middle, defended solidly.
On a length and on off, this is driven towards covers for one.
Goes fuller and on off,  this is defended back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Sticks to his line and length, Litton Das defends it solidly.
FOUR BYES! On a length and outside leg, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick but misses. The keeper gets a glove on it but couldn't get it. The ball goes past long stop for a boundary.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended towards backward square leg.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim pulls it towards mid-wicket for one.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out solidly.
On off, this is defended.
Goes fuller and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg.
Starts off with a wide one outside off, left alone.
Yet another one outside off, not played at.
Attacks the stumps this time, on middle, kept out.
Another harmless ball outside off, Rahim watches it go to the keeper.
FOUR! Easy for Rahim. Full and on the pads, this is clipped through square leg for a boundary.
On off, defended.
Goes fuller and on middle, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for one.
Back f the length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim eases it towards silly point.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Back of the length and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to defend it but misses as it hits his pads.
Sticks to his length bowling it outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim guides it towards point.
On a length and on off, Litton Das defends it towards silly point.
Sticks to his length and outside off, Litton Das leaves it alone. Slight halt in play as Litton Das looks uneasy and is struggling a bit with his eyes.
Back of the length and outside off,  Litton Das slaps it towards point and gets a single.
On a length and outside leg, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick it but misses. The keeper does well and gets a glove n it. Leg bye taken.
Fuller one on leg, Litton Das flicks it towards square leg for one.
Fuller and on off, this is flicked towards mid-wicket for one.
On off, this is blocked out.
Back of the length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended towards mid on.
On a length and on middle angling it inside, Mushfiqur Rahim gets an inside edge and the ball hits his pads.
Fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards square leg. A couple of runs taken.
FOUR! Fuller and on leg, Litton Das uses the pace of the ball and flicks it past backward square leg for a boundary.
On middle, blocked out solidly.
On a length and on middle, this is defended towards mid off.
Fuller and on middle, Litton Das nudges it towards mid-wicket and gets a couple of runs.
On a length and on middle, this is defended towards mid off.
On a length and outside off, Litton Das lets it go. The ball just aired past the off stump. That will be Stumps for Day 1.
Nice start from Fernando. Fuller length, shaping in from around off. Rahim keeps it out on the leg side.
Good bounce and carry. Length ball, on the fifth stump line, left alone by Rahim.
First runs of the day. Length, a bit wider and this is chopped through backward point for a quick single.
Fuller and into the channel outside off, Das lets it through to the keeper.
Around the top of off, punched away through covers for a run.
Goes fuller this time, around off. Rahim leans in and punches it towards covers.
Rajitha floats it up on the pads, Das looks to flick it away but closes the face of the bat a bit too early. Das gets squared up and gets a leading edge through point. They get one.
On a good length, close to the off pole. Rahim shoulders arms.
Rajitha looking to swing it away off the pads but the ball just skids on. Rahim clips it past square leg for a run.
Nicely bowled! Length, around off. This one nips back in sharply and there's a bit of an extra bounce as well. Assured leave from Litton Das but he is a bit surprised by the bounce.
Length again, on middle, tucked away to mid-wicket.
A touch fuller and on off, just skidding through. Das keeps it out.
Good running! On a good length over off, Rahim hops back and just bunts it out on the off side for a quick single.
On off, Das looks to drive on the up but mistimes it towards mid off.
This one keeps really low. This is outside off and the ball just doesn't rise up at all and Das is completely undone by it.
On a length, slanted into middle. Das nudges it onto the leg side.
Goes fuller this time, on off. Das punches it sweetly towards extra cover.
On middle, blocked out by Das.
Leg bye! A bit too straight from Rajitha, Rahim looks to flick it away but gets it off his pads down to fine leg for a leg bye.

Through him! A length ball, around off and this one just jags back in really sharply. There is extra bounce as well and Litton Das almost gets cut in half as the ball goes between bat and pad and just over the middle stump.
Outside off, tapped away towards covers for a quick single.

FOUR! Unlucky! Rajitha with a lovely outswinging yorker on off. Mushfiqur Rahim just about manages to get his bat down in time and the ball goes quickly past the fielder at first slip for a boundary. Really probing bowling this from Rajitha.
Fuller and angling into middle, Rahim tucks it towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Rajitha errs in line and pays the price. This is sliding down leg and Rahim just flicks it into the vacant fine leg fence.
On a length, outside off. Left alone.
Length again, around off. Das looks to cut but ends up chopping it back to the keeper.
Around the top of off, Das gets right behind the line to make the block.
Goes fuller and wider this time, Das just eases it through point for a single.
Fuller length, outside off. Rahim looks to cover drive off the front foot but mistimes it badly.
Short of a length, around the hips. Rahim dabs it down towards mid-wicket.
Fuller and on the fifth stump line, easy leave for Das.
Outside off and just a hint of shape away from the right-hander. Litton Das lets it through to the keeper. No ball called for overstepping as well.
Top of the off stump line, solidly kept out by Das.
Good-length, on leg stump. This is worked behind square on the leg side for a single.

Good delivery. This one lands on the fourth stump line and comes in sharply with the angle. Rahim strides out to pad it away but misses and the ball misses the off stump by a close margin as well. Kasun Rajitha cannot believe that one didn't nip back in enough to hit the stumps.
On off, blocked out.
Into the channel around off, Rahim leaves it alone.
Starts off with a flatter delivery on off. Das taps it towards cover-point.
Fuller and on off, driven straight to short cover.
Floated up, outside off. Litton Das uses his wrists to drive it towards sweeper cover and picks up a single.
Gives it a bit more air and bowls it on off. Rahim keeps it out.
This is drifted onto middle, Rahim defends it under his eyeline.
Drifted into middle and this one just straightens after pitching. Rahim defends it out with soft hands.

OUT! TAKEN! Sharp work from Kusal Mendis and Kasun Rajitha finally gets the breakthrough for his side. Length ball, around the top of off and seems to be coming in with the angle. The ball just holds its line and Litton Das has a tentative push at it. The ball takes the outside edge and Mendis takes a brilliant catch diving forward at first slip as the ball was just dying on him. A brilliant knock from Litton Das comes to an end and the partnership is broken at 272 runs. Rajitha's hard work finally pays off.
Howout: c Kusal Mendis b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: This is full and spilled down the leg side. Hossain looks to flick but misses.
On off, blocked out.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Kasun Rajitha has the five-wicket haul and what a well-deserved one it has been as well. Rajitha goes very full, close to the off pole and there's just a hint of away movement. Mosaddek Hossain is pushed onto the back foot as he looks to keep it out but there's no feet movement from him. The ball takes the outside edge and Niroshan Dickwella behind the sticks takes a good sharp catch. Hossain goes for a duck and Rajitha pulling things back nicely for Sri Lanka.
Howout: c Niroshan Dickwella b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: Rajitha comes from 'round the wicket to the left-hander and angles it into off. Islam defends it out.
Full and wide, Islam drives it to deep point and gets off the mark with a single.
Brilliant from the keeper. Shorter and down leg, Islam gets a bottom edge as he looks to pull it fine but Niroshan Dickwella gets a good right glove on it.
Pacy bumper this time from Fernando, over leg stump and Islam ducks under it.
This is just floated up on a length, going across the left-hander. Islam has a poke at it but is comprehensively beaten.
Back of a length, over middle. Taijul Islam hops it and keeps it down on the off side.
Full and on middle and leg, flicked away on the bounce towards short leg. The ball hits the arm of the fielder over there and the batters scamper through for one.
Nicely bowled! Tight line on off and just angling in. Rahim can only defend it out.
Beaten! Angled in on a length from outside off and the ball again just holds its line. Islam looks to drive but is beaten past the outside edge.
Goes fuller this time, around off. Islam pushes it back to the bowler.
Angled into off stump from 'round the wicket, just nipping away a touch after pitching. Islam edges it down towards gully.
Now Rajitha goes for the inswinger and almost gets his man. On a length and angling into middle. Islam is late on the shot and almost ends up getting a leading edge to the man at short cover.
Fuller and in that channel around off, stylish leave from Islam.
An effort delivery from Rajitha but he spills it down the leg side. Maiden over though.
Tossed up on middle, this is eased towards mid on for one.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
On middle, this is defended towards silly point.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended towards the mid on region.
Sticks to his line and length, Taijul Islam blocks it to mid on.
On a length and on middle, Taijul Islam pushes the ball back towards Praveen Jayawickrama.
Goes fuller and on middle, quicker too, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards covers.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it towards gully.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller and on leg, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.
FOUR! Back of the length, slightly shorter, Mushfiqur Rahim makes room for himself and cuts it between backward point and gully. The ball races past the fence for a boundary. 300 up for Bangladesh.
On off, this is blocked out.
Flatter and on leg, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it to mid on for one.
Fuller and on middle, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
Sticks to bowling it fuller, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards short leg.
On middle, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and hits it towards extra cover and gets a couple. Ohh, this is sloppy, an overthrow that costs them another run. Three runs taken.
On off, this is blocked out.
Goes fuller and on off, this i defended towards mid on.
FOUR! Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim with a reverse sweep as the ball races towards third man and past the fence.
FOUR! On a length and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim bends his knee and drives it past covers for a boundary. This is excellent batting from Mushfiqur Rahim.
Sticks to his line and length, this is pushed to covers for one.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller and outside off, Taijul Islam cuts it to point.
On middle, this is blocked out solidly.
FOUR! Fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim leans a bit and sweeps it towards backward square leg for a boundary.
Similar to last delivery, Mushfiqur Rahim again sweeps it towards backward square leg, this time for one. Moves to 149 with that single.
FOUR! Fuller and on middle, Taijul Islam makes room and uses his feet as he lofts it over mid-wicket for a boundary.
On off, this is blocked out.
Fuller and on middle, Taijul Islam uses his feet and defends it away.
On middle, this is defended towards mid on.
Fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards square leg and gets a couple. 150 up for Mushfiqur Rahim. This is excellent batting from Mushfiqur Rahim.
On off, this is defended towards covers.
Goes fuller and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards mid-wicket and gets a single.
On middle, blocked out.
Full toss down the leg side, Taijul Islam looks to slog sweep it but misses. The ball hits his pads. A loud appeal from Ramesh Mendis but the finger stays down.
Tossed up outside off, this is driven towards covers.
FOUR! Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it through point. The ball races past the fence for a boundary.
Fuller and down the leg side, this is defended towards short leg.
On off, defended.
Fuller and outside off, this is defended towards backward point. A quick single taken.
Fuller and outside off, this is driven towards covers. A couple of runs taken.
Shorter and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Shorter and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim pulls it and manages to keep it down. The ball races towards fine leg. No runs taken.
Another bouncer on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim ducks under it.
Shorter and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim pulls it and keeps it down towards fine leg.
Spicy short ball from 'round the stumps and over middle. This one zips through and Mushfiqur Rahim does well to sway his head away from the line of the ball.

Back of the length, Mushfiqur Rahim strikes it towards square leg. A quick single is taken. Ohh, it has hit the umpire as the fielder tries for a direct hit. It was always going well wide and thankfully the umpire is fine.
Tosses it up outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim guides it towards point and takes a single.
On a good length and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.

FOUR! Fuller and on off, Taijul Islam leans forwards and lofts it over mid on and also clears the man at long on who is standing well inside the ropes. The ball goes over the fence for a one-bounce boundary.
On middle, blocked out.
Similar to the last one, this is again, pushed towards the bowler.
Goes fuller again, this is blocked out.
Back of the length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
A length ball outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim raises arms and leaves it towards the keeper.
Change of length and on middle, this is blocked out solidly.
